title: Gasquet Village Subdivision Close to the River 300 Sierra
text:
Gasquet Village Subdivision Close to the River 300 Sierra ad date: 10/17/2015 
Close to the River 300 Sierra Wood Road, Gasquet, CA Spacious 2685 sq ft 4 bedrm 3 bath home plus 1248 sq ft of living area in daylight basement ideal for guest quarters or mother-in-law. Large master suite w/door to deck, master bath w/jetted tub, separate shower. Very large greatroom (w/woodstove & French doors to covered deck) open to dining, kitchen w/breakfast bar, newer oak flooring, tile counter tops, vaulted ceilings, located on a tree covered 1.67 acre parcel, easy walking distance to the Smith River. MLS 1500499 $369,000 Kurt Stremberg, Broker 785 E. Washington Blvd #2, Crescent City Office: 707-465-2121 Cell: 707-954-1732
